== Filemonak Pauluchem Potr ==
'''Epistle to Philemon'''


==== Filemonak Pauluchem Potr ====

Pauluk, poile pavtti roma xarant bondkhonnint ghalo tedna, to Onesimus mhonnlolea eka chakrak vollkhunk pavlo.  Frijiechea Kolos nograntlea Filemonak, aplea dhoniak,  Onesimus soddun ghel’lo.  Hea parpollak  Jesuchi vollokh diun Kristi dhormant bhitor kaddlea uprant,  taka portun tachea dhonia-xim dhaddunk,  Paulu bore sondik ravtalo.  63vea vorsa Koloskarank ek potr dhaddchem aslem tedna, hi sondi taka mell’li.  Tikikus Pauluchea niropia borabor,  Onesimus gelo.  Khotkhotit ulo marun,  Paulun aplea ixttak,  Filemonak, hem potr boroilem ani mhatmikponnan hea parpollak vagoi mhonn tache lagim maglem. 


